Name: Ahros: One Warrior Chronicle
About the game: Ahros: One Warrior Chronicle is an adventure VR-game that tells about a way of a young warrior, which is to restore peace and order in a world destroyed by global war. In this game, the story is told through a series of tasks that character performs with the help of: - Dragons - Stationary and mobile turrets - Various mechanisms - The character himself Join our @4ilab Twitter to see more news and updates.
